司经营业务，逐步退出运动鞋服业务。 2022 年7月，其所属公司泰富金谷通过购买贵人鸟集团(香港)有限公司的股份，以20.36%的股份成为贵人鸟控股股东，李志华成为实际控制人;8月12日，经董事会选举，李志华出任贵人鸟公司董事长。 根据贵人鸟早前公告，此次更名并非简单品牌重塑，而是战略发展规划的关键一环。 图源天眼查 潮新闻记者留意到，电商平台上主打销售东北大米的 “金鹤” 旗舰店，其背后所属企业是黑龙江和美泰富农业发展股份有限公司，该公司的法人代表为李志华。"},"attached_info":"CkEImrfrm4OWk7NrEAMaCTExMjg0MDY1MCCBuIi8BjAAOJADQARyCjkzMjA0NDQzNzB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"56 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-c578105396745f7b52f5b4323b1da7a9_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"5_1736816010.651256","card_id":"Q_7491524678","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":7491524678,"title":"为什么学会自行车后，几十年不骑都不会忘记这个能力？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/7491524678","type":"question","created":1734794593,"answer_count":98,"follower_count":355,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[404,1440,39051,169223],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"如题，一个人学会自行车后，几十年不接触自行车，在重新使用自行车时，依然能很快就熟练这个技能，这是什么机制造成的？人类还有哪些技能会用到相同的机制？"},"attached_info":"CkEImrfrm4OWk7NrEAMaCTExMjQ3NDkyNSDhupu7BjAAOOMCQAVyCjc0OTE1MjQ2Nzh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"51 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-d8fad38271eb011dcabb5f11f821b1a1_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"6_1736816010.651571","card_id":"Q_26012189","card_label":{"type":"new","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":26012189,"title":"如何用文字描述把食物写得更好吃？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/26012189","type":"question"